Packages

library(tidyverse)     ## data wrangling + ggplot2
library(fGarch)        ## data simulation
library(systemfonts)   ## custom fonts
library(colorspace)    ## adjust colors
library(RColorBrewer)  ## ColorBrewer palettes
library(rcartocolor)   ## Carto palettes
library(ggforce)       ## sina plots
library(ggdist)        ## halfeye plot
library(gghalves)      ## off-set jitter

Generate Data

file <- here::here("data", "data.Rds")

if (!file.exists(file)) {
  set.seed(5)
  data_1 <- tibble(group = 'Group A', value = fGarch::rsnorm(50, mean = 3.5, sd = 1, xi = 10))
  data_2 <- tibble(group = 'Group B', value = rnorm(15, mean = 4.5, sd = 1.0))
  data_3 <- tibble(group = 'Group C', value = rnorm(20, mean = 4.6, sd = 0.8))
  data_4 <- tibble(group = 'Group D', value = rnorm(4, mean = 4, sd = 0.5))
  
  data <- rbind(data_1, data_2, data_3, data_4)
  data$group <- as_factor(data$group)
  
  write_rds(data, file)
} else {
  data <- read_rds(file)
}

ggplot2 Setup

theme_set(theme_void(base_family = "Recia"))

theme_update(
  axis.text.x = element_text(color = "black", face = "bold", size = 26, 
                             margin = margin(t = 6)),
  axis.text.y = element_text(color = "black", size = 22, hjust = 1, 
                             margin = margin(r = 6), family = "Overpass Mono"),
  panel.grid.major.y = element_line(color = "grey90", size = .6),
  axis.line.x = element_line(color = "black", size = 1),
  plot.margin = margin(rep(20, 4))
)

Barplot

ggplot(data, aes(x = group, y = value)) +
  geom_col()


data %>% 
  group_by(group) %>% 
  summarize(mean = mean(value)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = group, y = mean)) +
  geom_col() 


ggplot(data, aes(x = group, y = value)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "summary")


ggplot(data, aes(x = group, y = value)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "summary", fun = "mean")

Save to Object

g <- ggplot(data, aes(x = group, y = value, fill = group)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "summary", width = .8) +
  scale_y_continuous(expand = c(0, 0), breaks = 1:4)

Add Colors (and Manipulate Them)

g + scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Set2", guide = "none")


RColorBrewer::display.brewer.all()


g + scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Dark2", guide = "none")


my_pal <- RColorBrewer::brewer.pal(4, "Dark2")
my_pal <- colorspace::darken(my_pal, .3)

g + scale_fill_manual(values = my_pal, guide = "none")


ggplot(data, aes(x = group, y = value)) +
  geom_bar(
    aes(fill = group, 
        fill = after_scale(colorspace::darken(fill, .2))),
    stat = "summary", width = .8
  ) +
  scale_y_continuous(expand = c(0, 0), breaks = 1:9 * .5) +
  scale_fill_brewer(palette = "Dark2", guide = "none")


rcartocolor::display_carto_all()


g + rcartocolor::scale_fill_carto_d(palette = "Bold", guide = "none")


my_pal <- rcartocolor::carto_pal(n = 5, name = "Bold")[1:4]

g + scale_fill_manual(values = my_pal, guide = "none")


set.seed(2021)
my_pal <- sample(rcartocolor::carto_pal(n = 6, name = "Bold")[1:4])

g + scale_fill_manual(values = my_pal, guide = "none")

Dynamite Plot

ggplot(data, aes(x = group, y = value, fill = group)) +
  geom_bar(stat = "summary", width = .8, color = "#212121") +
  stat_summary(
    geom = "errorbar",
    fun.max = function(x) mean(x) + sd(x),
    fun.min = function(x) mean(x) - sd(x),
    width = .3, size = .8, color = "#212121"
  ) +
  scale_y_continuous(expand = c(0, 0), breaks = 1:9) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = my_pal, guide = "none")


ggplot(data, aes(x = group, y = value, fill = group)) +
  stat_summary(
    geom = "errorbar",
    fun.max = function(x) mean(x) + sd(x),
    fun.min = function(x) mean(x) - sd(x),
    width = .3, size = .8, color = "black"
  ) +
  geom_bar(stat = "summary", width = .8, size = .8, color = "black") +
  scale_y_continuous(expand = c(0, 0), breaks = 1:9) +
  scale_fill_manual(values = my_pal, guide = "none")

Boxplot

g <- ggplot(data, aes(x = group, y = value, color = group, fill = group)) +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = 1:9) +
  scale_color_manual(values = my_pal, guide = "none") +
  scale_fill_manual(values = my_pal, guide = "none")

g + geom_boxplot(alpha = .5, size = 1.2)


g + 
  geom_boxplot(
    aes(fill = group, fill = after_scale(colorspace::lighten(fill, .5))),
    size = 1.5
  )


g + 
  geom_boxplot(
    aes(fill = group, fill = after_scale(colorspace::lighten(fill, .7))),
    size = 1.5, outlier.shape = NA
  ) +
  geom_point(
    position = position_jitter(width = .1, seed = 0),
    size = 7, alpha = .5
  )

  )


set.seed(2021)

g + 
  geom_violin(
    aes(fill = group, fill = after_scale(colorspace::lighten(fill, .7))),
    size = 1.2, bw = .2, width = .6, scale = "count"
  ) +
  stat_summary(
    geom = "point", 
    fun = function(x) median(x),
    shape = 23, size = 6, color = "black", stroke = 1.5
  ) + 
  ggforce::geom_sina(
    color = "black", maxwidth = .6, scale = "count", 
    size = 3, alpha = .5
  )

Raincloud Plots

g + 
  geom_boxplot(
    width = .2, fill = "white",
    size = 1.5, outlier.shape = NA
  ) +
  ggdist::stat_halfeye(
    adjust = .33, ## bandwidth
    width = .5, 
    color = NA, ## remove slab interval
    position = position_nudge(x = .15)
  ) +
  gghalves::geom_half_point(
    side = "l", 
    range_scale = .3, 
    alpha = .5, size = 3
  )


g + 
  geom_boxplot(
    width = .2, fill = "white",
    size = 1.5, outlier.shape = NA
  ) +
  ggdist::stat_halfeye(
    adjust = .33, 
    width = .5, 
    color = NA, 
    position = position_nudge(x = .15)
  ) +
  gghalves::geom_half_point(
    side = "l", 
    range_scale = .25, 
    alpha = .5, size = 3
  ) +
  coord_flip()


g + 
  geom_boxplot(
    width = .2, fill = "white",
    size = 1.5, outlier.shape = NA
  ) +
  ggdist::stat_halfeye(
    adjust = .33, 
    width = .5, 
    color = NA, 
    position = position_nudge(x = .15)
  ) +
  gghalves::geom_half_point(
    side = "l", 
    range_scale = .25, 
    alpha = .5, size = 3
  ) +
  coord_flip() +
  theme(
    axis.text.x = element_text(face = "plain", family = "Overpass Mono", size = 22),
    axis.text.y = element_text(face = "plain", family = "Recia", size = 26),
    panel.grid.major.x = element_line(color = "grey90", size = .6),
    panel.grid.major.y = element_blank()
  )


ggplot(data, aes(x = forcats::fct_rev(group), y = value, 
                 color = group, fill = group)) +
  geom_boxplot(
    width = .2, fill = "white",
    size = 1.5, outlier.shape = NA
  ) +
  ggdist::stat_halfeye(
    adjust = .33,
    width = .5, 
    color = NA,
    position = position_nudge(x = .15)
  ) +
  gghalves::geom_half_point(
    side = "l", 
    range_scale = .3, 
    alpha = .5, size = 3
  ) +
  coord_flip() +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = 1:9) +
  scale_color_manual(values = my_pal, guide = "none") +
  scale_fill_manual(values = my_pal, guide = "none") +
  theme(
    axis.text.x = element_text(face = "plain", family = "Overpass Mono", size = 18),
    axis.text.y = element_text(face = "plain", family = "Recia", size = 24),
    panel.grid.major.x = element_line(color = "grey90", size = .6),
    panel.grid.major.y = element_blank()
  )


g + 
  geom_boxplot(
    width = .2, fill = "white",
    size = 1.5, outlier.shape = NA
  ) +
  ggdist::stat_halfeye(
    adjust = .33, 
    width = .5, 
    color = NA, 
    position = position_nudge(x = .15)
  ) +
  geom_point(
    position = position_nudge(x = -.25),
